<span id="Description"></span>
==Описание==

The '''Solver CalculiX (new framework)''' command creates a SolverCalculix object, which uses the same framework as Elmer and Z88 solvers (the code is not visible for the user). It is preferred to use the original framework [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools.svg|32px]] [[FEM_SolverCalculixCcxtools|Solver CalculiX Standard]] because it contains extra checks, e.g. showing the elements with nonpositive Jacobian which might cause solution difficulties.

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Применение==

# Select {{MenuCommand|Solve → [[Image:FEM_SolverCalculiX.svg|16px]] Solver CalculiX (new framework)}} from the menu.

